Package com.intellij.facet

Interface FacetConfiguration

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppEngineFacetConfiguration, BuildoutFacetConfiguration, InvalidFacetConfiguration

    public interface FacetConfiguration
    Implementations of this interface contain settings of a specific facet.

    Implement PersistentStateComponent instead of overriding readExternal(Element) and writeExternal(Element) methods in your implementation of FacetConfiguration
